data.description: Explore this fantastic Mechanicsville townhome just minutes from downtown, dining, shopping, major highways, and public transport. Spanning four levels, this residence offers two bedrooms, two and a half baths, a 2-car garage, hardwood flooring, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry and jacuzzi tub in the owner’s suite.  The true highlight is the spacious rooftop terrace, providing stunning skyline views. This property is a must-see for those seeking a modern urban lifestyle with numerous conveniences and investment potential in a thriving community. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
